{"tid":2456152,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿加息 土耳其總統埃爾多安2年來第三度解僱央行行長","createTime":"2021-03-21T16:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T08:00:06.000Z","uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea16b0403acb2992fb9e273dbad9a6a0022ffe01","tid":2456152,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"路透社20日報道，央行18日曾加息200個基點，幅度超過市場預期。埃爾多安一直力推減息，2019年時他已說，高息率傷害經濟。央行行長18日的舉動，顯然不合總統心意。<br />\n<br />\n內文稱，央行加息是「前置」手段，旨在抑制通貨膨脹及支撐土耳其里拉匯率。<br />\n<br />\n阿巴爾在不足5個月前被委任，他上任後央行累計加息875個基點，政策利率達19%。<br />\n<br />\n政府宣布，新任央行行長為卡夫奇奧盧（Sahap Kavcioglu）。他是埃爾多安所屬正義與發展黨（AK Party）的前國會成員。<br />\n<br />\n報道提及，埃爾多安曾多次要求保持低利率。"},{"pid":"a0c8dd67542f93ccfd3a398c390f5418af0eb413","tid":2456152,"uid":306861,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b3e241405a558874a0c0177fa2773b72c389817","tid":2456152,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">Jay... Jay!!!!! JAY!!!!!!!!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"961554273c7fc5d15d2716b823182bb8b3644194","tid":2456152,"uid":351009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"5年貶值60%啫，仲有空間繼續印<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thsWYWf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthsWYWf.png&h=c8f73a09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51359b247565e03ce96a40927027ba36fe23bdda","tid":2456152,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:54:02.000Z","msg":"不如直接將唔準加息寫入憲法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3dbf8fe5d1f9fbc9e531926b24f705f88b342c","tid":2456152,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re